BAU_FxR0 = paste0(BAU_input,"..1/biomass/FX_R_SEED-0.tif") %>% raster()
BAU_FxR100 = paste0(BAU_input,"..1/biomass/FX_R_SEED-100.tif") %>% raster()

BAU_NFxR0 = paste0(BAU_input,"..1/biomass/NOFX_R_SEED-0.tif") %>% raster()
BAU_NFxR100 = paste0(BAU_input,"..1/biomass/NoFX_R_SEED-100.tif") %>% raster()

BAU_NFxNR0 = paste0(BAU_input,"..1/biomass/NOFX_NOR_SEED-0.tif") %>% raster()
BAU_NFxNR100 = paste0(BAU_input,"..1/biomass/NoFX_NOR_SEED-100.tif") %>% raster()

BAU_Shrub0 = BAU_FxR0 + BAU_NFxR0 + BAU_NFxNR0
BAU_Shrub100 = BAU_FxR100 + BAU_NFxR100 + BAU_NFxNR100

BAU_BMTot0 = paste0(BAU_input,"..1/biomass/TotalBiomass-0.tif") %>% raster()
BAU_BMTot100 = paste0(BAU_input,"..1/biomass/TotalBiomass-100.tif") %>% raster()

BAU_Covert0 = 1-(BAU_Shrub0/BAU_BMTot0)
BAU_Covert100 = 1-(BAU_Shrub100/BAU_BMTot100)

BAU_CovDif = BAU_Covert100-BAU_Covert0

Dont take into account the 0.

Biodiv = c("Year", "Scenario", "Spp_Rich_mean",  "Spp_Rich_min_surface",
           "Age_AVG_mean", "Age_AVG_min_surface",
            "Age_Richness_mean", "Age_Richness_min_surface")

Stack=stack()

for(year in seq(0, 100, by=10)){
  for(scenario in c("BAU","Adapty")){
    
    if(scenario == "BAU") {Input = BAU_input
    } else {Input = Adapty_input}
  
    SppRich = paste(Input,"..1/outputs/spp-counts/SPP-RICH-",
                       year,".img",sep="") %>% raster()
    SppRich[SppRich == 0] = NA
    SppRich_mean = cellStats(SppRich, stat='mean', na.rm=TRUE)
    Q = quantile(SppRich, probs = c(0.25, 0.75))
    f = freq(SppRich, merge=T) %>% as.data.frame()
    SppRich_Smin = f$count[which(f$value <= as.numeric(Q[1]))]%>% sum()
    
    if (year %in% c(0, 50, 100)){
      names(SppRich) = paste0("SppRich_",scenario,year)
      Stack = addLayer(Stack, SppRich)
    }
  
    AgeAVG = paste(Input,"..1/outputs/age-all-spp/AGE-AVG-",
                       year,".img",sep="") %>% raster()
    AgeAVG[AgeAVG == 0] = NA
    AgeAVG_mean = cellStats(AgeAVG, stat='mean', na.rm=TRUE)
    Q = quantile(AgeAVG, probs = c(0.25, 0.75))
    f = freq(AgeAVG, merge=T) %>% as.data.frame()
    AgeAVG_Smin = f$count[which(f$value <= as.numeric(Q[1]))]%>% sum()
    
    if (year %in% c(0, 50, 100)){
      names(AgeAVG) = paste0("AgeAVG_",scenario,year)
      Stack = addLayer(Stack, AgeAVG)
    }
    
    AgeRichness = paste(Input,"..1/outputs/age-all-spp/AGE-RICH-",
                       year,".img",sep="") %>% raster()
    AgeRichness[AgeRichness == 0] = NA
    AgeRichness_mean = cellStats(AgeRichness, stat='mean', na.rm=TRUE)
    Q = quantile(AgeRichness, probs = c(0.25, 0.75))
    f = freq(AgeRichness, merge=T) %>% as.data.frame()
    AgeRichness_Smin = f$count[which(f$value <= as.numeric(Q[1]))]%>% sum()
    
    if (year %in% c(0, 50, 100)){
      names(AgeRichness) = paste0("AgeRichness_",scenario,year)
      Stack = addLayer(Stack, AgeRichness)
    }
    
    Biodiv = rbind(Biodiv, c(year, scenario, SppRich_mean, SppRich_Smin,
                             AgeAVG_mean, AgeAVG_Smin, AgeRichness_mean,
                             AgeRichness_Smin))
    }
  }
  
colnames(Biodiv)=Biodiv[1,] %>% unlist %>% as.character
Biodiv=Biodiv[-1,] %>% as.data.frame()

j=c(1,3:8)

Biodiv[ , j] <- apply(Biodiv[ , j], 2,
                    function(x) as.numeric(as.character(x)))
Titles = c("Species richness", "Avrage age", "Age richness")

for(i in c(1:3)){
  Title = Titles[i]
  VarSatck = stack(Stack[[i]],Stack[[i+6]],Stack[[i+12]],Stack[[i+3]],Stack[[i+9]],Stack[[i+15]])
  Max = max(maxValue(VarSatck))+1
  Min = min(minValue(VarSatck))
  brks = seq(Min,Max,by=0.1)
  nbrks = length(brks)-1
  r.range = c(Min, Max)

  rasTot = sum(VarSatck)
  
  par(mfrow=c(2,3))
  for(i in seq_len(nlayers(VarSatck))){
    tmp = VarSatck[[i]]
    plot(tmp, breaks=brks,col=pal.2(nbrks), legend = F, zlim=c(Min,Max), 
    main = names(tmp))
    plot(rasTot, legend.only=TRUE, col=pal.2(nbrks),
       legend.width=1, legend.shrink=0.75,
       legend.args=list(text=Title, side=4, font=2, line=2.5, cex=0.8))
}}

Non parametric test and paired => Wilcoxon Test

shapiro.test(BAU_BDA$Mortality)
## 
##  Shapiro-Wilk normality test
## 
## data:  BAU_BDA$Mortality
## W = 0.96358, p-value = 0.007301
shapiro.test(Adapty_BDA$Mortality)
## 
##  Shapiro-Wilk normality test
## 
## data:  Adapty_BDA$Mortality
## W = 0.90035, p-value = 1.469e-06
Mortality_BAU = mean(BAU_BDA$Mortality)
sd_BAU = sd(BAU_BDA$Mortality)

Mortality_Adapty = mean(Adapty_BDA$Mortality)

wilcox.test(BAU_BDA$Mortality, Adapty_BDA$Mortality, paired=T)
## 
##  Wilcoxon signed rank test with continuity correction
## 
## data:  BAU_BDA$Mortality and Adapty_BDA$Mortality
## V = 3031, p-value = 0.002619
## alternative hypothesis: true location shift is not equal to 0

BAU_Clim = paste(BAU_input,"..1/Climate-future-input-log.csv",sep="") %>% read.csv()
BAU_FWI = cbind(BAU_Clim$Year,BAU_Clim$Timestep, BAU_Clim$FWI) %>% as.data.frame()
colnames(BAU_FWI) = c("Year", "day", "FWI")

list_year = BAU_FWI$Year %>% unique()

BAUgrp_FWI = c("Year", "FWI", "Min","Max")

for(year in list_year) {
  FWI = BAU_FWI$FWI[BAU_FWI$Year == year] %>% mean()
  Min = BAU_FWI$FWI[BAU_FWI$Year == year] %>% min()
  Max = BAU_FWI$FWI[BAU_FWI$Year == year] %>% max()
  BAUgrp_FWI = rbind(BAUgrp_FWI, c(year,FWI,Min,Max))
}

BAUgrp_FWI = as.data.frame(BAUgrp_FWI)
colnames(BAUgrp_FWI)=BAUgrp_FWI[1,] %>% unlist %>% as.character
BAUgrp_FWI=BAUgrp_FWI[-1,]
BAUgrp_FWI$Scenario = "BAU"

Adapty_Clim = paste(Adapty_input,"..1/Climate-future-input-log.csv",sep="") %>% read.csv()
Adapty_FWI = cbind(Adapty_Clim$Year,Adapty_Clim$Timestep, Adapty_Clim$FWI) %>% as.data.frame()
colnames(Adapty_FWI) = c("Year", "day", "FWI")

Adaptygrp_FWI = c("Year", "FWI", "Min","Max")

for(year in list_year) {
  FWI = Adapty_FWI$FWI[Adapty_FWI$Year == year] %>% mean()
  Min = Adapty_FWI$FWI[Adapty_FWI$Year == year] %>% min()
  Max = Adapty_FWI$FWI[Adapty_FWI$Year == year] %>% max()
  Adaptygrp_FWI = rbind(Adaptygrp_FWI, c(year,FWI,Min,Max))
}

Adaptygrp_FWI = as.data.frame(Adaptygrp_FWI)
colnames(Adaptygrp_FWI)=Adaptygrp_FWI[1,] %>% unlist %>% as.character
Adaptygrp_FWI=Adaptygrp_FWI[-1,]
Adaptygrp_FWI$Scenario = "Adapty"

FWI_Tot = rbind(BAUgrp_FWI,Adaptygrp_FWI)

FWI_Tot$Year = FWI_Tot$Year %>% as.numeric()
FWI_Tot$FWI = FWI_Tot$FWI %>% as.numeric()
FWI_Tot$Min = FWI_Tot$Min %>% as.numeric()
FWI_Tot$Max = FWI_Tot$Max %>% as.numeric()

FWIp = ggplot(FWI_Tot, aes(x=Year, y=FWI)) +
  geom_line() +
  xlab("year")+
  ylab("Mean fire weather index")+
  facet_wrap(~Scenario)

Minp = ggplot(FWI_Tot, aes(x=Year, y=Min)) +
  geom_line(color="blue") +
  xlab("year")+
  ylab("Min fire weather index")+
  facet_wrap(~Scenario)

Maxp = ggplot(FWI_Tot, aes(x=Year, y=Max)) +
  geom_line(color="red") +
  xlab("year")+
  ylab("Max fire weather index")+
  facet_wrap(~Scenario)

plot_grid(FWIp, Minp,Maxp, labels="AUTO", ncol = 1, nrow = 3)
